The paper deals with image translation using a generative model, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of a convolutional recurrent model architecture and the end-to-end training approach suggests that the paper may also fall under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves text processing and classification, which could place it under the sub-categories of natural language processing (cs.CL) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
